des: We realized we have amazing conversations first thing in the morning over breakfast (and...coffee!). Welcome to our flash briefing: a series of updates, conversations, and other shinanigans first thing in the morning with Adam and Noor. Listen to the couple talk about hustle, patience, philanthropy, culture, takes on news, and doing good while doing well, all over breakfast.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
